metadata.name: Unravel People's DOODLES
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's DOODLES, which represents an inactive state of pDOODLES. User can participate in a new DOODLES NFT acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's DOODLES as credit. upDOODLES can be claimed into pDOODLES when the subscription successfully acquires a new DOODLES NFT.
